	<h1 class="title">联合利华公布最新业绩，个人护理用品表现不错</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/343708/small/343708.jpg?1449500883" alt="">
