<div class="com-share" data-id="25563" data-title="《联合利华公布最新业绩，个人护理用品表现不错》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/25563/medium/25563.jpg?1460782568" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/25563.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
